  "2305380": {
    "name": "Attack on Hex Island",
    "steam_appid": 2305380,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款可爱且易上手的回合制卡组构筑/卡牌对战游戏，融合了《Tetra Master》《Triple Triad》和《宝可梦》的战斗系统。收集、升级并自定义你的队伍，策略性地击败对手，拯救他们免遭对“六角岛”的攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/c9e1319bbd80b58a7089b0c1c323a192.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/487ca48260ca38371698d50a637b65e8.poster.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/487ca48260ca38371698d50a637b65e8.webm?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/487ca48260ca38371698d50a637b65e8.mp4?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用箭头捕获对手的棋子并将其转化为你的颜色。比赛结束时，拥有最多己方颜色棋子的玩家获胜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当箭头相连时会触发战斗并掷骰子。战斗可能带来风险，但能通过连击获得额外捕获。元素属性对胜利至关重要，对弱势元素还能提供攻击加成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/11853ca4d306117a1e2095f223a9bc68.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/0e764da3e916416a84c8a2745c313e21.poster.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/0e764da3e916416a84c8a2745c313e21.webm?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/0e764da3e916416a84c8a2745c313e21.mp4?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现各种智胜对手、确保胜利的方法。有些棋子拥有独特的特殊能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/10198d06a4a30192f8b0004854a9f21d.poster.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/10198d06a4a30192f8b0004854a9f21d.webm?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/10198d06a4a30192f8b0004854a9f21d.mp4?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意棋盘上的墙壁、场地元素、炸弹等障碍物，它们也能为你所用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/cee430f049beedb9348da841a1d93f50.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/a64c4298a9e13c6440c2e43e42d45a20.poster.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/a64c4298a9e13c6440c2e43e42d45a20.webm?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/a64c4298a9e13c6440c2e43e42d45a20.mp4?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过战胜对手后掠夺、开启卡包和发现宝箱，扩展你的棋子和伙伴收藏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/99cffb47daddde151b2117de10ce4b35.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/89dc3c071054f9a7c2d80b0f9330da85.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >棋子拥有多样的设计、元素、能力和箭头组合，让你打造符合自己风格的独特队伍。你还可以升级和改造棋</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/9b666c34ad9cf6e9d939f821837d93f0.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/d0d81f641f846eef817f71010b7bfe01.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=373 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他玩家进行友好表演赛，或通过掠夺其全部棋子来检验友情！你可以按喜好自定义棋盘，或交给随机性并在对局中灵活调整策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/e6759a7b76d1c6f1f6b86ca6c973b10f.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/f2db76a3ecc8f0446f16732682cf8964.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=138 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入我们的 Discord 提出问题与反馈，并订阅我们的 YouTube 频道，了解我们下一步正在制作的游戏！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 俄语",
